<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd">
<concept id="concept_FEACCBC246744C0B83C2CD190FAE2A71"> 
  <title>Administration - Users and Groups</title> 
  <shortdesc>Manage user and group access to the Marketing Cloud, as well as
	 identity types, password policies, and login restrictions. 
  </shortdesc> 
  <prolog> 
	 <metadata> 
		<keywords> 
		  <keyword>audience services</keyword> 
		</keywords> 
		<othermeta name="solution" content="Marketing Cloud"/> </metadata>
  </prolog> 
  <conbody> 
	 <p> 
		<menucascade> 
		  <uicontrol>Marketing Cloud</uicontrol> 
		  <uicontrol>Tools</uicontrol> 
		</menucascade> 
	 </p> 
	 <p> 
		<image href="graphics/tools_menu.png"
		 id="image_92F420208DB54C59A49802541DE45C5F"> <?xm-replace_text Paragraph?>
		</image> 
	 </p> 
	 <table id="table_D52B582DB57B418EB9B5B449C7A2C745"> 
		<tgroup cols="2"><colspec colnum="1" colname="col1"
		  colwidth="1.00*"/><colspec colnum="2" colname="col2" colwidth="2.24*"/><thead> 
			 <row> 
				<entry colname="col1">Element 
				</entry> 
				<entry colname="col2">Description 
				</entry> 
			 </row></thead> 
		  <tbody> 
			 <row> 
				<entry colname="col1"> 
				  <p>User Management 
				  </p> 
				</entry> 
				<entry colname="col2"> 
				  <p>Add users to your organization. Emails are sent to invited
					 users. 
				  </p> 
				  <p>See 
					 <xref href="users.xml#concept_54E77D5A22E64307BCB4AB2510A6450F"
					  format="dita" scope="local"><?xm-replace_text User Management?></xref> 
				  </p> 
				</entry> 
			 </row> 
			 <row> 
				<entry colname="col1"> 
				  <p>Group Management 
				  </p> 
				</entry> 
				<entry colname="col2"> 
				  <p>Create a group, and users to the group. You can enable access
					 to a solution at the group level. For example, you can create a group that has 
					 <keyword>Analytics</keyword> rights, and add users to the
					 group. 
				  </p> 
				  <p>See 
					 <xref
					  href="groups.xml#concept_418F1B6DA1904E1CB316103F350BE3A8" format="dita"
					  scope="local"><?xm-replace_text Group Management?></xref> 
				  </p> 
				</entry> 
			 </row> 
			 <row> 
				<entry colname="col1"> 
				  <p>Identity 
				  </p> 
				</entry> 
				<entry colname="col2"> 
				  <p>View and manage identity types, password policies, and login
					 restrictions. 
				  </p> 
				</entry> 
			 </row> 
		  </tbody> 
		</tgroup> 
	 </table> 
	 <note>Before sending an email invitation to a 
		<keyword>Marketing Cloud</keyword> user, you must add the new user via 
		<menucascade><uicontrol>Tools</uicontrol><uicontrol>User
			 Management</uicontrol></menucascade>. Removing a user from the Marketing Cloud
		does not remove the user from other solutions, such as 
		<keyword>Target</keyword> or 
		<keyword>Analytics</keyword>. 
	 </note> 
	 <p>See 
		<xref href="link_accounts.xml#concept_DFCB29A3B4834FC59AA29E0BBA301584"
		 format="dita" scope="local"><?xm-replace_text Join the Marketing Cloud?></xref>
		for information about linking a solution log-in to the Adobe ID. 
	 </p> 
  </conbody> 
</concept> 
